Package software.kes.kraftwerk.choice

Class ChoiceBuilder1<A>

  • java.lang.Object
    • software.kes.kraftwerk.choice.ChoiceBuilder1<A>
  • Type Parameters:
    A - the type of the first choice
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ToGenerator<A>
    public final class ChoiceBuilder1<A>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ToGenerator<A>
    A builder to facilitate the construction of Generators that yield ChoiceN values.

    Use one of the or(software.kes.kraftwerk.Weighted<? extends software.kes.kraftwerk.Generator<? extends B>>) methods to add more choices, and call toGenerator() to build the final Generator.

    All instances of ChoiceBuilder are immutable and can be reused, even after calling toGenerator.
